cff-version: 1.2.0
title: sovereign-vault
abstract: >
  Reversible PII tokenization for LLM pipelines. Replaces sensitive values
  with HMAC-bound placeholder tokens so cloud AI can reason about cross-entity
  relationships without seeing real data. Three detection layers: regex,
  GLiNER NER, and Ollama contextual sweep. GDPR and HIPAA compliant.
